---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-[#080607] py-8 mt-16">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
      <!-- Payments -->
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 opacity-70">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-1.png" alt="Visa" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-2.png" alt="Mastercard" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-3.png" alt="Bitcoin" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-4.png" alt="USDT" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-5.png" alt="Ethereum" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-6.png" alt="Qiwi" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
        <img src="/img/logo-payments-7.png" alt="YooMoney" class="h-8 object-contain" loading="lazy">
      </div>

      <!-- License info -->
      <div class="text-center text-text-dim text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        <p>Лицензия Curacao № 8048/JAZ2021-047 (Antillephone N.V.)</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Играйте ответственно. Азартные игры доступны только для лиц старше 18 лет.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Copyright -->
      <p class="text-text-dim text-sm font-semibold">
        © 2023–{currentYear} 7K Casino. Все права защищены. 18+
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
